{"type":"article","id":850,"title":"今晚吃生命面包！精神上与抗争者们同在。","uid":4931,"topics":[6,291],"contents":"感来源于品葱上有人问“拿生命面包蘸海底捞是什么滋味”。才发现生命面包与香港理工大学的联系。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/12284\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/question/12284</a><br>\n今晚吃生命面包，虽然蘸不起海底捞。虽然人身在墙内，但精神上我与香港抗争者们同在！<br>\n<br>\n让大家明白生命面包代表什么：<br>\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E9%BA%B5%E5%8C%85\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E9%BA%B5%E5%8C%85</a><br>\n<br>\n<b>今晚到货的生命面包</b><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dby5qCL.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dby5qCL.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dby5qCL.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/soJ9TSB.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/soJ9TSB.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/soJ9TSB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<b>乳包乳包乳包乳包</b><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/0qMEOq8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0qMEOq8.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/0qMEOq8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/iOJrY39.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iOJrY39.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/iOJrY39.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n在这次之前，我都没听说过嘉顿还有生命面包这种东西，对于膜油和葱油们来说我还是Too young。说实话，生命面包比我以前买的面包都要好吃，乳包以后格外香甜。但生命面包的精神知道的人却不多，我只希望这把火能在墙内升起来。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nEp8aBr.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nEp8aBr.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nEp8aBr.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n光复中华，时代革命！","date":"2019-12-03","agreeCount":17,"discussionCount":0}